ogy and geoscience; and land services. Further, it provides digital delivery and advisory services, such as GIS-enabled asset control kits, AI-enabled feasibility and due diligence studies, asset conditions monitoring and controls, predictive lifecycle cost analysis, rate studies, and interactive digital twin. The company was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Reston, Virginia.", "fullTimeEmployees": 2139, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Gary P. Bowman", "age": 69, "title": "Founder, CEO & Director", "yearBorn": 1956, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 774134, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Bruce J. Labovitz", "age": 57, "title": "Executive VP & Chief Financial Officer", "yearBorn": 1968, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 902347, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Robert Alan Hickey", "age": 67, "title": "Chief Legal Officer & Secretary", "yearBorn": 1958, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 577475, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Daniel  Swayze", "title": "Executive VP & Chief Operating Officer", "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Matthew  Mullenix", "title": "EVP, Chief Information Officer & Chief Information Security Officer", "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. MK  Gribbons", "title": "Chief Human Resources Officer", "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Ronald M Robison", "title": "Principal and Director of Environmental Sciences Group", "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Vijay  Agrawal P.E.", "title": "Executive VP of National Ports & Harbors Practice", "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Andrew Robert Dearing", "title": "Executive Vice President", "fisc